00:34:31,900 --> 00:34:33,580
 Warts and all.

704
00:34:33,580 --> 00:34:36,340
 The whole package.

705
00:34:40,700 --> 00:34:42,540
 You will not gain access to him

706
00:34:42,540 --> 00:34:44,860
 or find answers to your prayers

707
00:34:44,860 --> 00:34:47,740
 in your prideful self-reliance.

708
00:34:47,740 --> 00:34:49,980
 Our self-reliance will kill us.

