00:34:49,980 --> 00:34:53,580
 Number two.

710
00:34:53,580 --> 00:34:59,940
 Weakness shows off God's strength.

711
00:34:59,940 --> 00:35:03,380
 It's what it does.

712
00:35:03,380 --> 00:35:05,380
 Weakness shows off God's strength.

713
00:35:05,380 --> 00:35:08,460
 I said earlier that God is attracted to those

714
00:35:08,460 --> 00:35:10,460
 who have nothing to contribute.

715
00:35:10,460 --> 00:35:11,420
 Why?

716
00:35:11,420 --> 00:35:12,260
 Why is that?

717
00:35:12,260 --> 00:35:14,980
 Why is he inclined to those people

718
00:35:14,980 --> 00:35:17,540
 over the people who think they have something to contribute?

719
00:35:17,540 --> 00:35:18,380
 Why is that?

720
00:35:18,380 --> 00:35:19,220
 Here's why.

721
00:35:19,220 --> 00:35:24,220
 Because when I contribute nothing to God except my need,

722
00:35:24,220 --> 00:35:27,860
 then God must contribute everything else.

