00:37:39,820 --> 00:37:44,820
 It should be exploding and bursting out because you can't,

773
00:37:44,820 --> 00:37:48,340
 but you serve the God who can.

774
00:37:48,340 --> 00:37:52,380
 That's who we serve, and that gives us such a confidence.

775
00:37:52,380 --> 00:37:54,180
 When things are the most hopeless,

776
00:37:54,180 --> 00:37:55,380
 that's when there's the most hope.

